<item>
            <title>[WFLY-7322] LDAP referrals does not work in Elytron ldap-realm</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-7322</link>
                <project id="12313721" key="WFLY">WildFly</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;LDAP referrals cannot be used in Elytron &lt;tt&gt;ldap-realm&lt;/tt&gt;. Ldap Realm is currently not prepared to work with referrals at all:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;ldap-realm&lt;/tt&gt; does not include any options which enable working with LDAP referrals (PicketBox use &lt;tt&gt;baseFilter&lt;/tt&gt; option which can be configured to return also referral object)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;implementation of &lt;tt&gt;org.wildfly.security.auth.realm.ldap.LdapSecurityRealm&lt;/tt&gt; does not include any logic which handles referrals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Referrals are important feature of LDAP. It has to be covered by Elytron =&amp;gt; requested blocker flag.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
