&lt;p&gt;, I am able to log in as user of referred server. (After appliing &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.jboss.org/browse/ELY-663&quot; title=&quot;LDAP referrals does not work - dir-context.referral-mode is always ignored&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;ELY-663&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;ELY-663&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-7320&quot; title=&quot;LDAP referrals does not work - need to set custom filter&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WFLY-7320&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WFLY-7320&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; patches)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13307858" author="olukas" created="Mon, 17 Oct 2016 09:10:40 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;In case when Elytron is able to work with referral based on added filter-name then no additional logic for &lt;b&gt;follow&lt;/b&gt; will be needed in the code.&lt;/p&gt;

