                            <comment id="13313987" author="honza889" created="Mon, 31 Oct 2016 05:19:53 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.jboss.org/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dlofthouse&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dlofthouse&quot;&gt;Darran Lofthouse&lt;/a&gt; Do we need &lt;b&gt;throw&lt;/b&gt; mode of LDAP referrals support? If we will follow every referral, it will be equivalent of &lt;b&gt;follow&lt;/b&gt; mode.&lt;br/&gt;
Issue can be set as resolved if throw mode is not required.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
